✓P4 2025@s11:
  Commit b07d891, dossier predictions_2025/
  Scan: 581 ch, 348.0M #p, 108.3M paires non-zero
  P4 = activity_A × activity_B × (1 - cooc_norm) × |z_uzzi|
  z_uzzi = (observed - E) / std, E = works_i × works_j / total_works_sum
  Top 10K INTER-espèces + INTRA classés par P4 score
  Matrice collision 9×9: CS×Physics (82), Humanities×Physics (72), CS×Humanities (56)
  Analyse top 100 INTER: 18 BANAL (18%), 30 INTÉRESSANT (30%), 41 WTF (41%), 11 BRUIT (11%)
  20/20 vérifications web positives, 0 faux positif
  BRUIT = artefacts tagging OA (Nucleofection, TSG101, Dysgeusia, etc.)
  Pipeline: step1_full_scan → step1_merge → step2_species_full → step3_p4_both → step4_report → step5_collision
✓GL@s12:
  Script: engine/analysis/glyph_laplacian.py (~350 lignes)
  64 glyphes = eigenvecteurs du Laplacien normalisé (D^{-1/2} W D^{-1/2})
  Matrice: snapshot_2015_65k.npz (cutoff 2015), log1p-transformée
  eigsh K=64 en 130s via LinearOperator (zero-copy CSC transpose)
  Blind test: R@100=70% (14/20), R@1K=85%, R@10K=100%
  d=8.78 (×20 vs P4 0.44), p=2.76e-12, median rank=8
  7 percées au rang 1 (AlphaGo, GPT, CAR-T, Microbiome, GAN, Liquid biopsy, Gravitational waves)
  Score spectral: Score(i,j) = Σ_k λ_k × v_k(i) × v_k(j)
  Chaque prédiction = formule (décomposition en top-5 glyphes contributeurs)
  3.3K prédictions inter-espèces, zero-cooc only
  Outputs: data/scan/glyphs.json, spectral_predictions.json, spectral_embeddings.npy, spectral_blind_test.json
  Innovations mémoire: deferred scipy imports, streaming float64→float32 from zip, zero-copy CSC transpose
